README.md

Awesome

   Delightful npm packages that make you say "wow, didn't know that was
   possible!" PRs welcome!

peer-to-peer

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/peerwiki]peerwiki - all of wikipedia
       on bittorrent
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/simple-peer]simple-peer - send
       video/voice/data p2p in the browser (with webrtc)
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/torrent-docker]torrent-docker -
       realtime boot of remote docker images over bittorrent
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/torrent-mount]torrent-mount - mount
       a torrent as a filesystem
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/webtorrent]webtorrent - streaming
       torrent client for node & the browser

browserify

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/brfs]brfs - turn fs.readFileSync()
       calls into inlined static assets
     * [https://gist.github.com/defunctzombie/4339901]browser field spec -
       replace certain files/modules when a module is bundled for the
       browser
     * [https://npmjs.org/package/browserify]browserify - use require() in
       the browser
     * [https://github.com/stackgl/glslify]glslify - npm modules compiled
       into WebGL shaders
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/webworkify]webworkify - composable
       web workers for browserify

files

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/file-type]file-type - detect file
       content types by checking their magic numbers
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/fuse4js]fuse4js - write filesystem
       driver in js

geometry

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/alpha-shape]alpha-shape - any
       dimensional alpha shapes (think "concave" hull)
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/box-intersect]box-intersect - fast
       any dimensional box intersection detection
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/convex-hull]convex-hull - robust any
       dimensional convex hull
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/delaunay-triangulate]delaunay-triang
       ulate - robust any dimensional delaunay triangulation
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/surface-nets]surface-nets - extracts
       level sets in any dimension
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/voronoi-diagram]voronoi-diagram -
       any dimensional voronoi diagrams
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/voxelize]voxelize - voxelize a mesh

hardware

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/cylon]cylon - command robots,
       devices, and more from node

images

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/indico.io]indico.io - facial emotion
       recognition and facial feature extraction
     * [https://trackingjs.com/]trackingjs - computer vision on the web

sound

     * [https://github.com/DanielRapp/doppler]doppler - detect motion with
       the doppler effect using only the microphone and speakers
     * [https://github.com/mattytemple/speak-js]speak.js - text-to-speech
       on the web

streams

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/strip-html]strip-html - strip html
       from a stream

text

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/diff]diff - show text differences
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/franc]franc - detect the language of
       text
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/indico.io]indico.io - political
       sentiment analysis
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-tesseract]node-tesseract - A
       simple wrapper for the Tesseract OCR package
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/normit]normit - Google translate
       text & speak it
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/ocrad.js]ocrad.js - OCR in
       Javascript via Emscripten
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/pullquoter]pullquoter - pull
       interesting quotes out of an article
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/sbd]sbd - split text into sentences
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/sentiment]sentiment - basic
       sentiment analysis

terminal

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/minimist]minimist - simple argument
       parser
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/progress]progress - create a simple
       terminal progress bar
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/terminal-menu]terminal-menu - create
       retro terminal menus
     * [https://github.com/dthree/vantage]vantage.js - CLI + SSH + REPL
       for Node
     * [https://github.com/dthree/cash]cash - Cross-platform Linux
       commands in pure ES6

virtual machines

     * [https://github.com/fcambus/jsemu]jsemu - A list of emulators
       written in the JavaScript
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/jslinux]jslinux - x86 emulator for
       running Linux, written in JavaScript
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/node-jvm]jvm - java virtual machine
       in pure node.js
     * [https://github.com/plasma-umass/doppio]doppio - actively updated
       jvm in node.js, written in TypeScript

misc

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/bell.js]bell.js - real-time
       anomalies detection for periodic time series.
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/bitcoinjs-lib]bitcoinjs-lib -
       bitcoin client for node & the browser
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/fastparallel]fastparallel - zero
       overhead parallel function calls
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/google-distance]google-distance -
       calculate travel distance between two locations on earth using
       Google Maps' API
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/qr-image]qr-image - generate QR
       codes

meta-programming

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/package/notevil]notevil - javascript
       javascript interpreter, useful for running untrusted code safely.

mad scientists (people)

     * [https://www.npmjs.com/%7Emikolalysenko]Mikola Lysenko - linear
       algebra, computational geometry, WebGL
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/%7Edominictarr]Dominic Tarr - streams,
       distributed systems
     * [https://www.npmjs.com/%7Etmpvar]Elijah Insua - NC machines,
       CAD/CAM
     * [https://github.com/mafintosh]Mathias Buus - torrents in node, fuse
       bindings, data replication
     * [https://github.com/feross]Feross Aboukhadijeh - webtorrent,
       bittorrent, p2p hacks
     * [https://github.com/maxogden]Max Ogden - streams, voxels, data
       replication

